name: 2048variants
body:
List of some 2048 variants:

The easy game, [10](http://orangefreeze.github.io/10/) 1+1=2 gameplay.

My newest game, [99](http://orangefreeze.github.io/99/) 11+11=22 gameplay.

Special thanks to [Asher Vollmer](http://asherv.com/threes/) for creating Threes.
